description: Table: Cli -  Contains per-cell Client Information, including timestamps, cell identification, and client-specific data attributes.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp of data record), Area_Name (geographic area of the cell), CellId (unique identifier for the cell site), Id2 (redundant cell identifier), Id3 (likely a client identifier, value 1 in sample), Id4 (likely another client identifier, value 1 in sample), vsDataType (data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (version of the data format), Cli.idleTimer (client idle timer value), Cli.cliId (client identifier).
